OWF Server

  The Ozone Widgeting Framework (OWF) is a set of tools used for organizing and displaying web applications 
  (widgets) in a single browser window.  It consists of the OWF Server, the {{{owf-security/index.html}OWF Security}}
  modules and an optional CAS Server.
  
  More detailed information can be found in the documents in the {{{downloads.html}Downloads}} section.  There
  is also an "all in one" bundle available that provides a fully self-contained instance of the OWF, including
  optional security modules and the CAS Server.